  "body": "Feature request:\r\n\r\nI've encountered a problem while using this plugin: I need to **specify the destination folder** for the compiled contracts (some params depend on the chain), but I can't since the **path is hardcoded**. It's fairly simple to solve, just adding an optional param for the path and defaulting it to the actual path should make it, I guess I could even do it myself.\r\n",
